{"tid":705769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一周必看】 傳奇酒保見盡名人逸事　長住半島酒店60年","createTime":"2018-06-17T12:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T13:49:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5f8fa8c409d4977e264f9c7740566dd2cd2263","tid":705769,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:45:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180617/20423189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180617%2F20423189&d=qk5jPCq5806TQkVFI%2BHgWOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=8aea82ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180617%2F20423189&h=389b46a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180617/20423189</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月17日 <br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\n傳奇酒保見盡名人逸事　長住半島酒店60年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「嗱呢度睇明星呢真係一清二楚，邊個架車喺度、上車追蹤都好清楚，哈！」站在半島酒店一樓閣樓，77歲高級調酒師鍾金雄（Johnny）像個大頑童般指向大堂茶座，瞇起雙眼笑道。由1957年入職半島酒店至今，大半生奉獻給這位「遠東貴婦」，在Johnny雙眸中，哪些風景最難忘？拉開酒吧大門小酌一杯，聽他娓娓道來那些已逝年代的美好片刻。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n今日焦點‧即聽<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【一周必看】遭家人棒打鴛鴦　尼泊爾男等足港女10幾年"},{"pid":"47ae3f2caf76ba536e8af5a872d7dbd3dce5344e","tid":705769,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"無聊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明星咪又係人一個。只有八婆先會睇娛樂版"},{"pid":"11a4de219f9ee65cc4a75c33807d3e857c04845e","tid":705769,"uid":3698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:49:38.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題好似好撚多野睇咁<br />\n入黎得幾句無內容既廢話"}]}